# Quick Reference

## Essential Commands

### Development
```bash
# Start local development
npm run dev

# Start local Supabase
npx supabase start

# Run tests
npm run test

# Lint
npm run lint
```

### Deployment
```bash
# Deploy to Fly.io (source token first)
source vault/occ/fly/api_token.env
fly deploy --app [app-name]

# Check deployment status
fly status --app [app-name]
fly logs --app [app-name]
```

### Git Workflow
```bash
# Check status before working
git status -sb

# Create feature branch
git checkout -b [role]/[type]/[description]

# Stash for shutdown
git stash push --include-untracked -m "shutdown-YYYY-MM-DD"
```

